\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
This class provides an empty implementation of \mbox{\hyperlink{interfaceit_1_1unical_1_1mat_1_1parsers_1_1asp_1_1clingo_1_1ClingoParserVisitor}{Clingo\+Parser\+Visitor}}, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
